{"tid":2232183,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「天能」有冇人覺得因為要從後座開前座門 所以依條女先做到女主角？","createTime":"2020-10-06T08:17:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T02:05:57.000Z","uid":42246,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5b2a58ef8287fe2ae22c7791e4fa182575801ce8","tid":2232183,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T08:17:02.000Z","msg":"依一幕全球女演員應該得佢做到<br />\n<br />\n佢就因為咁所以先做到天能女主角<br />\n<br />\n所以成套戲既女主角根本就係隻80寸長腿而唔係個位女演員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n算唔算係個位女演員既天能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知我講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nwhat done is done <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a44530cfd1e188f1cf0dab0de47cd2da7e2ac2","tid":2232183,"uid":42246,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T08:21:20.000Z","msg":"隻腳長到拎到來篤波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca51c34a1f214abc5b52f29b522a8f4060d2e74","tid":2232183,"uid":42246,"like":